text: Hmmm.....
It seems like Diver Neville has lost...
Well then, I guess it's my turn!
Everyone, CHARGE!!!
I think I see a boat coming towards us...
Hey, you know where this is?
The Bipole Sea, nearing Nolavillia.
Oh god, what do I do now...
This is pretty far away from Altar, right?
I was escaping from there but then a storm hit me and I ended up here.
Is is okay if you could take me to whereever you're going?
We're going to Nolavillia to retrieve the Holy Itucher.
I'm warning you, it could get dangerous.
Wait, why would you want the Itucher?
It like destroyed Altar Town and stuff.
Well, some evil scientists have gotten it and the world is in danger.
The world is in danger?
I guess I should probably help you stop that.
[Recruit ???] (Q) Recruit (W) Do not recruit
Okay...
